{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":9,"day":28}],"page_start":4,"page_end":4,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"伟大的舵手〔对口词〕","authors":["河北省农民业余演出队"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海航行靠舵手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闯险滩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠舵手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过急流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠舵手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绕暗礁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠舵手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠舵手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是我们最伟大的舵手！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那黑云密布的岁月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那战火纷飞的年头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席挥巨手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写下了雄文四卷；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发出了战斗的号令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开辟了革命的大路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里江山风雷吼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们工农兵群众，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿起枪杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥起斧头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把三座大山推翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要把一穷二白赶走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力量的源泉来自何处？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自我们伟大领袖毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱敬爱的毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次又一次接见了百万文化革命大军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧握着文化革命大军战士们的手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔着千山万水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞向毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔着千里万里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸向毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席呀毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你和文化革命大军战士们握了手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是握了我们的手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱贫下中农心里热血滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱贫下中农眼里热泪流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱手上，都是劲儿；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱手上，热呼呼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要用这双钢铁巨手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改造世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重整地球！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席，伟大的舵手！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们跟着您闹革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢教日月换新天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披荆斩棘向前走！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指河，河让路！指山，山低头！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大寨路上不停步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社万里铺锦绣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席，伟大的舵手！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您号召开展无产阶级文化大革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要向牛鬼蛇神开火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同阶级敌人大搏斗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把旧世界，打它个人仰马翻！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把旧世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砸它个落花流水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让红旗漫天飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让红光照五洲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创造新世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大步向前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走！走！走！！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}